Turkish Singer Ibrahim Tatlises Shot, Hurriyet Newspaper Says

-- B y   S t e v e   B r y a n t
-- 
2011-03-14T06:28:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/turkish-singer-ibrahim-tatlises-shot-hurriyet-newspaper-says.html
Ibrahim Tatlises, the Turkish
singer who  owns  restaurants and a television production company,
was shot in the head as he left studios in Istanbul, Hurriyet
newspaper reported.  Tatlises was in intensive care at a hospital in the city
after three emergency operations overnight, the newspaper
reported.  Five men in a black car opened fire with Kalashnikov
rifles, hitting Tatlises and wounding his assistant Buket
Cakici, the newspaper reported.   Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
